The paper deals with measuring and editing material appearance, which is a topic related to computer graphics (cs.GR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of large-scale subjective ratings and machine learning techniques also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of the proposed control space for human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
